data.description: Spacious ranch home, built in 2002 and situated back off the road, on two lots equaling (approx.) .70 acre+/-. This home offers 1560 sq. ft. of living space with a nice and easy layout; beginning with an open and inviting entry, the living room is off to the right offering plenty of natural light, and down the hall are two nice sized bedrooms, one full bath with a double vanity sink, and an Owner's suite with full bath. The heart of the home features a large, warm and open kitchen/dining room with plenty of beautifully refinished cabinets and Pergo wood flooring. The exterior features a rear gravel parking area, a spacious front porch that's perfect for watching the parades across the street, there is a rear spacious two tier wood deck and two car attached garage with shelving units. Updates within the last five years include: Tub/toilet/faucet in owner's bathroom, new ceiling fans throughout, Pergo wood floors in entry, dining and kitchen areas, wood planks have been replaced on the rear deck, kitchen recessed lighting installed, refinished kitchen cabinets and new sink, new rear sliding door with enclosed blinds, and a brand new 98% energy efficient furnace and a/c unit. This one will go fast, call your agent today. This home has public water and sewer.
